      "writtenOn": "2019-01-09T02:07:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i think this should remain swarming_tags because ChromeOS is asking for builder-level tags to annotate builders with domain-specific stuff.\n\nAlternatively, we can leave this as is, but repurpose later when builder gains builder-level tags.\n\nWDYT?",
      "range": {
